B.aFU=new A.d6("capital_bank","Capital Bank Mobile \u2013 Jordan","Capital Bank\u2019s advanced mobile application covers daily banking needs using modern and secure technologies.\n\nMain features:\n\u2022 View and manage accounts from the dashboard.\n\u2022 View and manage beneficiary accounts.\n\u2022 Perform local and international transfers.\n\u2022 Pay bills through eFAWATEERcom.\n\u2022 Transfer instantly using CliQ.\n\u2022 Manage credit cards and pay installments.\n\u2022 Manage profile, biometrics, contact number, loyalty points, and cardless cash withdrawals.\n\u2022 Communicate securely with the bank team 24/7.","Capital Bank\u2019s all-new and advanced mobile application covers all your daily banking needs using state-of-the-art technologies to help make your life simpler.","",B.a_I,B.cd,B.im,"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.capital.cbt","https://apps.apple.com/jo/app/capital-bank-mobile-jordan/id1630681705","https://capitalbank.jo/","com.capital.cbt")
