B.aFM=new A.d6("blink","Blink App","Blink is a digital banking app that covers day-to-day banking needs in one mobile experience.\n\nMain benefits:\n\u2022 Open an account digitally in minutes.\n\u2022 Get an instant virtual debit card after account creation.\n\u2022 Receive a physical card delivered for free.\n\u2022 Send and receive money instantly.\n\u2022 Issue a virtual credit card and shop online.\n\u2022 Use cardless withdrawal and deposit.\n\u2022 Access online account and card statements.\n\nBlink focuses on a paperless, queue-free, and hassle-free digital banking journey.","Your entire day-to-day banking needs in one app. Get your free virtual debit card immediately upon opening your account and spend away.","",B.a2_,B.cd,B.im,"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.blink.cbt","https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-blink/id1607969058",null,"com.blink.cbt")
