B.aFJ=new A.d6("moe","MOE App","The Ministry of Education in the UAE introduces its mobile app to improve the level and variety of services it provides MOE mobile app is a channel for the public to benefit of the e-Services provided by the Ministry of Education. Through its user-friendly interface, you can request services related to General Education (eg. Attestation Services, Certificate equivalency services, Verify the authenticity of equivalency or attestation of certificates, Inquiries, Suggestions, and Complaints features) among other various services. In addition to educational services, MOE mobile app provides many features such as Follow up application status, Access & download result documents of an application, Ministry News Feed, Contact Info, Frequently Asked Questions, MOE Services Guidelines, Inquiry, Complaints, and suggestion services\u2026 etc.","Government mobile application released on Google Play and App Store.","assets/images/projects/MOE_UAE.png",B.a4X,B.cd,B.io,u.C,u.L,null,"ae.gov.moe.mobileservices")
